  "reference_number": "RUS3044",
  "remarks": "\nAymani Nesievna KADYROVA is an “involved person” under the Russia (Sanctions) (EU Exit) Regulations 2019 because she is or has been\n involved in destabilising Ukraine or undermining or threatening the territorial integrity, sovereignty or independence of Ukraine by engaging in and providing support for the Government of Russia’s programme for the military-patriotic re-education of Ukrainian children in the TOT’s through her role as President of \nThe Akmat Kadyrov Foundation. \n",
